data.description: This beautiful 4-bedroom 2.5 bath with a 2-car garage is located near the Government Canyon State Natural Area, in the north west region of Helotes off Galm Road. Contact me directly by phone 518-309-2488. Buyer’s agents are welcome with pre-approved clients. This home features 2352 square feet of living space on a lot size of 4,791 Sq ft. The first floor offers a grand entry way with high ceilings leading to a separate dining room and hallway connecting a powder bath and utility room. The home is upgraded with a new Owens corning dimensional roof and Culligan water softer system, complimented with a reverse osmosis unit. The entry hallway also flows into a large eat-in kitchen and breakfast nook that extends to a covered patio. Off the breakfast area is a spacious living room, perfect for entertaining! The master suite, located off the living room, offers a nice master bath with walk-in closet. Contact me directly by phone 518-309-2488.
data.whatILove: We love this family-oriented neighbourhood with top rated schools, and access to north west theme parks and military bases.
